      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot Garden ¶ 29/8/70 ¶  ¶ This day, dear Mr Birch, I learnt from my countryman, Mr Schneider of Tambo, ¶  that you also lately heard of the presense of a white man among the nomadic tribes b...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.08.29a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Charles Birch</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Item IC 846928 74/1714, Queensland State Archives.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">29/8/70</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This day, dear Mr Birch, I learnt from my countryman, Mr Schneider of Tambo,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Qld.</p>
               </note> that you also lately heard of the presense of a white man among the nomadic tribes beyond the Thomson River,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Qld.</p>
               </note> and that you anticipate this poor errant being is a survivor of Leichhardts party.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also E. Schneider and C. Birch to M, September 1870 (in this edition as 70-09-00b), and D. Lewis (2013), pp. 253ff.</p>
               </note> As I take a deep interest in the fate of the missing explorer and his companions, I beg of you to leave nothing within your power undone to bring in this white man, and to unveil thus the fate of Leichhardt. It is now a good season to do so; the enormous fall of rain has filled all the waterholes and thus the central portions of Australia, can this year (as far as supply of water is concerned) be traversed with facility. I really believe that two good bushmen with two natives would set the matter at rest in one month. If the white man was rescued, and proved to be one of Dr Leichhardts companions, (and who else can it be be<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Word repeated in going from one line to the next.</p>
               </note>?) then a <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">large reward</hi>
               </seg> would easily be collected by subscription</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>So pray, do what you can. It is a honorable task that devolves on you.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With my best regards</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller, M.D.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I will see personally that the rescue of this white man remains not unrewarded.</p>
         </div>
